text: Olga Moroz is a Belarusian archer. Moroz competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics. She was born on 9 December 1966.Volha Zabuhina- Moroz == References == Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian archers Category:Olympians for Belarus
